        p.event Christian Aid Carol Service - Tuesday 9th<br> Starts at 18:00
        .event-details Join us for a joyful and heartfelt evening of traditional carols, readings, and community spirit in support of Christian Aid. Gather with friends and family in the beautiful setting of St Mary’s Church, Bideford, as we celebrate the hope and light of the Christmas season while raising awareness for those in need around the world. Everyone is welcome.

